Modelled (losely) after PAM, provide a system that allows programs to
perform access checks for users using Grimoire Ability Lists.

Library that can load modules for access control.

Module that uses RuneStone to provide network transparency compatible
with Grimoire.

Module that reads Ability Lists from a file.

Module that reads Ability Lists from LDAP according to the same rules
as Grimoires' LdapAbility does ATM.

Daemon that uses RuneStone to provide Merlins' services to the above
mentioned network transparency module.

Daemon that uses the library and http://www.dazuko.org/ to provide the
access control system to the Linux Kernel.

